        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">The only UK agency working exclusively on AI search visibility. Tests across all six major AI platforms (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, Google AI). Proprietary Five Signal Model framework built from 1,400+ UK business audits. Based in Colchester, Essex, serving Yorkshire businesses remotely. Ecosystem services from GBP 800/mo.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Strengths:</span> Only agency working exclusively on AI search. Proprietary methodology. Original research data. Transparent pricing. Tests all six platforms.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
